
<div class="upper">

  <div class="content">

    <div class="headline">

      <h1><span class="bold">So much more</span> than just a scholarship.</h1>
      <h5 class="grey">We believe that kids attending under-resourced schools in low-income communities need more support than simply financial aid.</h5>

      <div class="button scroll-start" scroll-target="#lower">
        Find Out More
        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-down"></span>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div><!-- /content -->
</div><!-- /upper -->

<div id="lower" class="lower">

  <div class="content">

    <div class="section what-we-do">


      <div class="text">

        <h4>Hoku Scholars (formerly Waianae Coast Scholarship Fund) is an <span class="bold">integrated</span>, merit-based scholarship program that helps kids from America's <span class="bold">most vulnerable communities</span> get into college.</h4>
      </div>

      <div class="image">
        <%= image_tag "WCSFcheck.jpg", :alt => "A few of our kids" %>
      </div>


    </div><!-- /what-we-do -->

    <div class="section attributes clear">

      <div class="question">

        <h4>How do <span class="bold">Hoku Scholars perform?</span></h4>

      </div>

      <div class="row clear">

        <div class="attribute academic">

          <div class="wrapper">

            <%= image_tag "icons/academic.jpg", :alt => "Academic Achievement" %>
            <h3>Academic Achievement</h3>
            <p>Hoku scholars average a 3.83 GPA. All students are enrolled in the proper college-required courses and on pace to pass AP level courses.</p>

          </div>

        </div>

        <div class="attribute extracurricular">

          <div class="wrapper">

            <%= image_tag "icons/extracurricular.jpg", :alt => "Extracurricular" %>
            <h3>Extracurricular</h3>
            <p>100% of Hoku Scholars are involved in extracurricular activities, with 53% of scholars holding leadership roles.</p>

          </div>

        </div>


      </div>

      <div class="row clear">

        <div class="attribute service">

          <div class="wrapper">

            <%= image_tag "icons/service.jpg", :alt => "Community Service" %>
            <h3>Community Service</h3>
            <p>The average Hoku Scholar completes 32 hours of service per year. Each student leads a community service initiative that impacts their community.</p>

          </div>

        </div>

        <div class="attribute test">

          <div class="wrapper">

            <%= image_tag "icons/test.jpg", :alt => "Test Prep" %>
            <h3>Test Prep</h3>
            <p>Each Hoku Scholar must pass a quiz for every tested benchmark on the ACT/SAT prior to their junior year. 100% of the students will take the PSAT. </p>

          </div>

        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="attribute pdu">

        <div class="wrapper">

          <%= image_tag "icons/pdu.jpg", :alt => "Professional Development" %>
          <h3>Professional Development</h3>
          <p>Hoku scholars complete 2 professional development workshops every semester spanning topics such as communication skills, financial assistance applications,
            and selecting fit-appropriate colleges.</p>

          </div>

        </div>

      </div><!-- /attributes -->

      <div id="stayUpdated" class="section">
        <div class="text">
          <h3 class="">Stay updated</h3>
          <div>We are constantly adapting and improving our program. If you want to stay current on what we are doing, sign up to receive email updates.</div>
        </div>

        <!-- Begin MailChimp Signup Form -->
