              <div>We are young and very passionate about what we do but can't do this alone. If you would like to get involved or can help us out in any way, don't hesitate to send us an <a href="mailto:directors@hokuscholars.org">email!</a></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div><!-- /.modal-content -->
    </div><!-- /.modal-dialog -->
  </div><!-- /.modal -->

